
ALL Platform => https://gorails.com/setup/


• Rails & Ruby on Macos ---------------------------------------

    brew install rbenv ruby-build
    rbenv install 2.7.2
    rbenv global 2.7.2
    gem install rails -v 6.0.3.4
    rbenv rehash
    brew install yarn
    
    brew install postgresql
    brew services start postgresql

    rails new myapp -d postgresql
    cd myapp
    rake db:create

        --> It might raise an error. If so : https://stackoverflow.com/questions/13573204/psql-could-not-connect-to-server-no-such-file-or-directory-mac-os-x

            brew uninstall postgresql
            brew doctor
            brew cleanup
            rm -r /usr/local/var/postgres
            rm -r /Users/henri/Library/Application\ Support/Postgres
            brew install postgresql
            brew services start postgresql
            rake db:create
    
    rails server -b "0.0.0.0" -p 3001


